Package: Coralysis
Type: Package
Title: Coralysis sensitive identification of imbalanced cell types and states in single-cell data via multi-level integration
Version: 1.0.0
Description: Coralysis is an R package featuring a multi-level integration algorithm for sensitive integration, reference-mapping, and cell state identification in single-cell data.
